---
layout: layouts/base.njk
permalink: /
eleventyNavigation:
  key: Home
  order: 1
---

<div class="space-y-8 mt-4">
  <div class="py-6">
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-emerald-950/50 border border-emerald-500/30 text-emerald-400 text-xs font-mono font-bold tracking-wider uppercase mb-4">
      <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-400 animate-pulse"></span>
      QRV • Station Online
    </div>
    
    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black tracking-tight text-white max-w-2xl leading-none">
      Welcome to my <br>
      <span class="text-amber-500">radio exploits</span>
    </h1>
    
    <p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-400 max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
      This is home base for my amateur radio journey — portable ops, antenna experiments, contest memories, and honest gear reviews from the shack and the field.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
      <a href="/blog/" class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-amber-500 hover:bg-amber-600 text-slate-950 font-bold rounded-lg shadow-lg shadow-amber-500/10 transition text-sm">
        Read the logbook
      </a>
      <a href="/gallery/" class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 border border-slate-700 text-slate-200 font-medium rounded-lg transition text-sm">
        View gallery
      </a>
    </div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
    
    <div class="md:col-span-2 bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-6 backdrop-blur">
      <h2 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-amber-500/90 font-mono mb-4">Station Snapshot</h2>
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-slate-800/60 py-2 text-sm">
        <span class="text-slate-400">Callsign</span>
        <span class="font-mono font-bold text-slate-200">M7KQX</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-slate-800/60 py-2 text-sm">
        <span class="text-slate-400">Location</span>
        <span class="text-slate-200">Warrington, UK (IO83qk)</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="bg-slate-900/40 border border-slate-800/80 rounded-xl p-6">
      <h3 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-cyan-400 font-mono mb-4">Recent Activity</h3>
      
      <div class="space-y-3">
        {%- for post in collections.posts | reverse | batch(3) | first -%}
          <div class="border-b border-slate-800/60 pb-2 last:border-0 last:pb-0">
            <a href="{{ post.url | url }}" class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-200 hover:text-amber-500 transition block">
              {{ post.data.title }}
            </a>
            <span class="text-xs font-mono text-slate-500 block mt-0.5">
              {{ post.date | readableDate }}
            </span>
          </div>
        {%- else -%}
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 italic">No logs found in posts folder.</p>
        {%- endfor -%}
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>